00:49:25.317 --> 00:49:26.276
BATAS SA KARAPATANG PANTAO

00:49:29.863 --> 00:49:31.865
Gusto mo bang maging isang pro bono na abogado?

00:49:31.948 --> 00:49:32.866
Oo.

00:49:32.949 --> 00:49:35.327
-Hindi kapani-paniwala 'yan.
-Hindi naman.

00:49:37.704 --> 00:49:38.747
Mayroon bang espesyal na dahilan?

